summary: Detective Pikachu is definitely good now ⊟ This one piece of merchandise, coming to the Pokemon Center website in April,...
caption:
Detective Pikachu is definitely good now ⊟

This one piece of merchandise, coming to the Pokemon Center website in April, justifies the whole operation, regardless of your opinion of weirdly detailed and weirdly Reynoldsed creatures. I want the Pikachu deerstalker hat.

I don’t know when I’d wear it, but I’d like to. Just like I’m happy to possess the Scribblenauts and Sonic the Hedgehog plush hats I have in my closet for very specific occasions that I haven’t identified yet.

► THE NEW CLUB TINY IS HERE  Support Tiny Cartridge!

even a 30 dollar game deserves a legitimate ending
body:
The End of Detective Pikachu

Garbage.

SPOILERS AHEAD FOR THOSE WHO CARE:

.

.

.

.

.

.

You start the game with one sole mission: find your missing dad.

And you know what you don’t fucking do at the end? FIND THE MISSING GOD-DAMNED DAD. At MOST you find out the fact that he’s at least alive from MewTwo. There were hints of malecious and even murderous intent directed toward the dad. BUT GOLLY-GEE GUESS I JUST GOTTA WAIT TO SEE IF THERE’S A SEQUEL. 🙄
